snippet.title: TRIHAYWBFRFYH Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The world ends in 20 minutes.

Play the game at http://gamejolt.com/games/other/trihaywbfrfyh/20342/

Soundtrack available at http://connorsherlock.bandcamp.com/

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

TRIHAYWBFRFYH features writing by H.P. Lovecraft,

and voice work by:

JSmithOTI - http://www.youtube.com/jsmithoti
Calistman222 - http://www.youtube.com/calistman222
Rebecca Lamarche - http://www.imdb.com/name/nm5734680/?ref_=fn_al_nm_1
Emmett Sherlock - https://soundcloud.com/emmettsherlock
